                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-238-off1280 t18190915-238-cd1281"></join>, one pocket-book, value 7 s.; four pieces of foreign gold coin, value 20 s., and two sovereigns, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190915-238-victim2031" type="victimName">
